OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1779898263
OL,3,CHospital shuts nearly half of
OL,4,Coperating theatres due to heatwave
OL,5,Cfault
OL,7,FSome planned procedures have been
OL,8,Fpostponed at Jersey's General Hospital
OL,9,Fdue to a major fault caused by the
OL,10,Fextremely hot weather.
OL,12,FThree out of its seven operating
OL,13,Ftheatres have been closed following a
OL,14,Fmechanical issue, but officials stress
OL,15,Fthat all emergency, urgent and
OL,16,Fmaternity care will carry on as normal.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1779898263
OL,3,CHospital shuts nearly half of
OL,4,Coperating theatres due to heatwave
OL,5,Cfault
OL,7,FSimon West, the Medical Director of
OL,8,FHealth and Care Jersey, adds that the
OL,9,Fhospital has cancelled some elective
OL,10,Fsurgeries "as a precaution" and "there
OL,11,Fis no risk to patient safety".
OL,13,FAny affected patients will be
OL,14,Fcontacted directly, while external
OL,15,Fcontractors are being brought in to
OL,16,Fhelp with repairs.
OL,18,FIt is unclear how long the issue will
OL,19,Flast, while Mr West has apologised for
OL,20,Fthe disruption.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1779898263
OL,3,CHospital shuts nearly half of
OL,4,Coperating theatres due to heatwave
OL,5,Cfault
OL,7,FHe explains: "Each patient is being
OL,8,Fclinically reviewed and prioritised,
OL,9,Fensuring those with the greatest need
OL,10,Fcontinue to receive care as quickly as
OL,11,Fpossible.
OL,13,F"While there may be a short-term
OL,14,Fimpact on waiting times, rebooking is
OL,15,Falready underway and every effort is
OL,16,Fbeing made to minimise delays."
OL,18,FJersey is currently in a heatwave,
OL,19,Frecording the hottest May day on
OL,20,Frecord three times in a row.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1779898263
OL,3,CHospital shuts nearly half of
OL,4,Coperating theatres due to heatwave
OL,5,Cfault
OL,7,FHealth officials have not declared a
OL,8,Fmajor incident - unlike neighbouring
OL,9,FGuernsey, which announced a critical
OL,10,Fsituation at the Princess Elizabeth
OL,11,FHospital on Tuesday due to high demand
OL,12,Ffor beds unrelated to the current hot
OL,13,Fweather.
OL,15,FHowever, Mr West does admit that the
OL,16,Fissues in Jersey can be a symptom of
OL,17,Fworking in an ageing hospital.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1779898263
OL,3,CHospital shuts nearly half of
OL,4,Coperating theatres due to heatwave
OL,5,Cfault
OL,7,FPlans to build the long-awaited new
OL,8,F#710 million facility at Overdale have
OL,9,Fstalled, with "no guarantee" that a
OL,10,Fcontract will be signed by the
OL,11,FGovernment ahead of June's election.
OL,13,FThe Medical Director says: "While this
OL,14,Fis not a major incident, it does
OL,15,Fhighlight the challenges that can
OL,16,Farise in an ageing hospital facility,
OL,17,Fparticularly during periods of
OL,18,Funusually warm weather.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1779898263
OL,3,CHospital shuts nearly half of
OL,4,Coperating theatres due to heatwave
OL,5,Cfault
OL,7,F"Additional support measures are in
OL,8,Fplace, including portable air
OL,9,Fconditioning units ... ice pops across
OL,10,Fservices to help staff and patients
OL,11,Fstay cool and comfortable, alongside
OL,12,Faccess to cold drinks and rest areas."
OL,14,FMr West also praised healthcare staff
OL,15,Ffor their hard work during the
OL,16,Fheatwave and thanked patients for
OL,17,Ftheir understanding.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
